topic.body:
Final Turing test. I'm cleaning up ZeroTalk. Starting over.
&nbsp;
They could be after me this time, but it's not the cops. I cannot be put in a mental institution. The mission to prevent the heat death of the universe is too important.
&nbsp;
Then again, let's not weaponize AI. That's a .. pretty bad idea. I've seen the future, and come back to the past .. as if god had given me a second chance at life. Now is the time to get it right.

1524972133_1CcoRvm8AhLxYLtYoXwwzobh74Kzc.body:
And that's the theory of everything.
&nbsp;
Shit. I better get better.. so I can give my speech sometime next week.
